{"MANY":[{"def":"A retinue of servants; a household.","pos":""}],"MANY-MINDED":[{"def":"Having many faculties; versatile; many-sided.","pos":""}],"MANY-SIDED":[{"def":"In many different ways; variously.","pos":""}],"MANYPLIES":[{"def":"The third division, or that between the reticulum, or honeycomb stomach, and the abomasum, or rennet stomach, in the stomach of ruminants; the omasum; the psalterium.","pos":""}]}